00:55:04.560 --> 00:55:06.360
Okay. Thank you.

00:55:19.760 --> 00:55:23.280
Wanneung, what’s wrong?

00:55:25.560 --> 00:55:26.680
Calm down.

00:55:26.720 --> 00:55:28.320
Khun Win…

00:55:28.360 --> 00:55:29.600
Tell me what’s wrong.

00:55:30.040 --> 00:55:31.040
Khun Win…

00:55:31.080 --> 00:55:33.120
P’ Waanwaan called to say I got the movie.

00:55:33.120 --> 00:55:36.760
And not just that…I’ll be in the same film as you.

00:55:38.840 --> 00:55:41.560
I’m so excited.

00:55:41.560 --> 00:55:43.600
The reason I got this role

00:55:43.640 --> 00:55:46.320
is because P’ Waanwaan pushed for me.

00:55:46.360 --> 00:55:49.880
Otherwise, I’d never have come this far.

00:55:51.720 --> 00:55:53.320
I’m in a movie.

00:55:57.240 --> 00:56:00.000
Aren’t you happy for me?

00:56:02.520 --> 00:56:04.000
Congratulations, Wanneung.

00:56:05.600 --> 00:56:07.000
Khun Win.

00:56:15.480 --> 00:56:17.080
I’m in a movie.

00:56:19.480 --> 00:56:22.680
Yay. Finally.

00:56:42.440 --> 00:56:43.880
Khun Win?

00:56:45.280 --> 00:56:46.400
Khun Win.

00:56:52.240 --> 00:56:55.200
Khun Win, I can’t sleep.

00:56:55.240 --> 00:56:56.320
What’s wrong?

00:56:56.400 --> 00:56:58.840
I’m still too excited.

00:56:58.920 --> 00:57:00.000
Can I sleep in your room?

00:57:00.000 --> 00:57:01.120
Can I sleep in your room?

00:57:02.640 --> 00:57:04.080
Please?

00:57:04.080 --> 00:57:05.160
Please.

00:58:26.960 --> 00:58:28.080
Khun Win.

00:58:31.920 --> 00:58:33.760
I’m really happy.

00:58:34.080 --> 00:58:37.240
So happy I can’t even put it into words.

00:58:38.080 --> 00:58:39.240
You know…

00:58:39.280 --> 00:58:42.120
my dream is getting closer and closer.

00:58:43.080 --> 00:58:45.720
And do you know what makes me happiest?

00:58:47.480 --> 00:58:48.680
What?

00:58:50.720 --> 00:58:54.520
You’re in that dream with me.

00:58:57.800 --> 00:58:58.960
Wanneung.

01:02:15.400 --> 01:02:17.320
We’re not running, no yoga.

01:02:17.440 --> 01:02:18.800
We’re going swimming.

01:02:18.840 --> 01:02:20.280
No, Win.

01:02:20.520 --> 01:02:21.520
Don’t.

01:02:22.040 --> 01:02:25.000
If one day Win still feels scared,
even knowing it’s risky,

01:02:25.040 --> 01:02:26.360
but still wants to try…

01:02:26.520 --> 01:02:29.320
that’s the day Win falls in love
with that person.

01:02:30.160 --> 01:02:33.280
A superstar like Win Pawee
dating a superstar like me

01:02:33.360 --> 01:02:36.560
is far more appropriate than
dating a supporting role like you.

01:02:36.600 --> 01:02:38.160
May and I aren’t anything anymore.

01:02:38.200 --> 01:02:39.680
- We broke up.
- You don’t have to explain.

01:02:39.680 --> 01:02:41.640
We’re not anything to each other.

01:02:41.680 --> 01:02:45.160
Wanneung and I are dating.

01:02:45.400 --> 01:02:47.720
Two, two.

01:02:48.760 --> 01:02:50.600
- Cut.
- You’ve got charm.

01:02:52.280 --> 01:02:55.120
Getting choke-held all the time.

01:02:55.680 --> 01:02:57.520
You’re enjoying it.

01:02:57.520 --> 01:02:59.240
- Yes.
- Raw chicken.

01:02:59.280 --> 01:03:00.000
Then don’t eat it raw.

01:03:00.000 --> 01:03:01.040
Then don’t eat it raw.

01:03:02.600 --> 01:03:04.040
This is fun.

01:03:04.080 --> 01:03:07.200
- I was wondering if it would stand up.
- It can stand.

01:03:07.760 --> 01:03:09.640
Belle…

01:03:10.400 --> 01:03:12.600
Belle’s going to throw up.

01:03:12.960 --> 01:03:14.280
How do I get down?

01:03:14.280 --> 01:03:15.920
I’ll carry you.